Package odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne

package odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ACMTrainer
    The ACMTrainer Program generates a training arff file by adding the document signature of a supplied document to an existing arff file.
    ArffDocument
    An Arff Document contains the assigned category and document signature of a file used in training a Learning Machine (SVM).
    ArffGenerator
    An Arff Generator generates an arff file from a list of Documents.
    ArffParser
    An Arff Parser reads in the text from an arff file and constructs a list of Arff Documents from the data in that text.
    ClassifyDocument
    A Classify Document contains the raw text, assigned category, and document signature of a file that will be classified by a Learning Machine(SVM).
    ClassifyParser
    A Classify Parser reads in the raw text from a file and constructs a Classify Document from that text.
    Document
    A Document is a general object used for storing a document's raw text, category, and functional signature.
    InitialTrainer
     
    LearningMachine
    A Learning machine uses a WEKA SMO (SVM) to retrieve a predicted category for each Classify Document.
    StopList
    A StopList contains a list of stopwords (insignificant words).
    TrainDocument
    A Train Document contains the raw text, assigned category, and document signature of a file used in training a Learning Machine (SVM).
    TrainParser
    A Train Parser reads in the raw text from a file and constructs a Train Document from that text.
    VocabCollection
    A VocabCollection holds words that are significant to those documents used for training.
    WordFrequency
    Contains the document frequency and inverse document frequency of a word.
    WordInfo
    Contains the count, normalized count, and term weight of a word found in a document.
